data.description: Welcome Home to 638 Wedgewood Drive this is the home you have been waiting to find! This charming 4 Bedroom / 3 Bathroom, split foyer home is  in the heart of  the coveted community of Eagle Watch in Woodstock. The well designed main level boasts hardwood flooring, a beautiful living room with a vaulted ceiling.  3 bedrooms on the main level and modern kitchen with granite counters. The primary suite on the main level offers a large relaxing retreat with a large jetted tub, separate shower, double vanity and so much more.  Downstairs offers the versatile and spacious teen suite/in-law suite or guest room with a full bathroom. The large back deck is perfect for enjoying a cup of coffee, entertaining or just relaxing.  The Eagle Watch community amenities are top notch! Eagle Watch has a golf course, swimming pools, tennis courts, playground, fitness center and basketball courts. Close to downtown Woodstock, schools, restaurants and shopping. Seller Offering $5,000 in closing cost with full price offer. Make your appointment today!
